<paragraph id="8BD0DB4AFFD8C954EFD3FE6CFBABC9BB" blockId="5.[174,1233,349,505]" pageId="5" pageNumber="416">
<collectionCode id="ED7E438FFFD8C954EFD3FE6CFF32C99C" box="[227,242,456,478]" country="Chile" name="Departamento de Geologia, Universidad de Chile" pageId="5" pageNumber="416">R</collectionCode>
e f e r r e d m a t e r i a l. Besides the 
